data.description: VILLA SERENA is a quiet gated community with a pool, fitness center, and park area to relax. All this is centrally located, just North of Bloomingdale and 301. This unit is near the back of the community diagonally across from the community center. Access to the property is through the 1 car garage or side door. Walking up the stairs you feel at home with the open layout and high ceilings. The kitchen is to the right, the dining room is to the left and the large living room is open to the screened lanai giving you the natural Florida feel.  The split bedroom design allows for privacy when needed.  Centrally located just off of Blooming Dale, 301 and I75 shopping, restaurants, schools, and parks are a short distance away. Tampa, beaches, and airports are within a reasonable drive with many avenues to get there. Come and make this property your home as you tailor it to your taste.
